latestPosts.caption:
When I first picked up a cricket bat, I wasn’t trying to prove a point. I was just a young girl who loved the game.
But back then, there were no stadiums cheering for women’s cricket. No headlines. Just questions:
“Why cricket?” “For a girl?” “Is this even a real career?”

Still, I showed up every day, with nothing but belief.

That same belief, the hausla to keep going, is what makes #HauslaTalks by @kotakbankltd so special.
It’s a series that shines a light on real people who backed themselves when no one else did.

Their stories remind me of my own journey, and they’re proof that courage and conviction can take you further than you ever imagined.

Catch these inspiring stories now on @kotakbankltd ‘s YouTube channel.

#Collab #HauslaTalks #HauslaHaiTohHoJayega #Inspiration #WomensCricket #MustWatch #KotakMahindraBank

For me, cricket has always been more than just a game. That’s why I’m so excited to share something special with you today, a really cool project by my friends at @batery_ai where you could win an evening with me and @yuvisofficial ✨

They’ve created an extraordinary collection of collectible cards featuring iconic cricket moments. 🏏

To make this even more special, I’d like to giveaway one of my collectible cards to one of my amazing followers!

Here’s how to participate:
✨Make sure you’re following me and @batery_ai. 
✨ Share this post on your stories.
✨ Drop a comment below, tell me your favourite cricket memory or why you’d love the card!

Can’t wait to see who wins this special card and a chance to join us for the Meet & Greet.

I hope it brings you as much joy as cricket has always brought me. Good luck, and let’s celebrate our favourite game together!

#Ad #Partnership
